						               													<description>The most desired (limited edition) sneakers are launching soon! Gather your friends to queue up and buy the sneakers! Suit up, warriors. This is War and get as many shoe boxes as possible!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players are scalpers and play with cards. Players who collect shoeboxes with 20 points will win the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There are sneakers cards, queuer cards and action cards. Sneaker card shows the condition to get scores, i.e. the queuer card limit and also the points which can be taken. Queuer cards and action cards are for your hand management.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Random players begin to play clockwise and each player will choose one colour of queuer cards and action cards. They will be divided into 2 card decks. Each player draw 2 queuer cards and 2 action cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During your turn, player can play the queuer card concealed and below the sneaker card. If there are already queuer cards present, put below the last queuer card and queue up. Player may also choose to use action cards to fight against others, to increase own queuer numbers or create chaos. Once the queue vacancy of particular sneaker is full, reveal all queuer cards in this row and check the total queuers of each colour. Player can get points in form of shoeboxes and stack them up (There are 72 mini shoeboxes figure). Any player who collects shoeboxes with 20 points will be the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
